From Geno Subject Re The doctrine of Original Sin Joseph Buehler writes This all obviously applies equally well to infants or adults since both have Infants must be baptized therefore or they cannot enter into They too need this form of life in them or they cannot enter into Are you saying that baptism has nothing to do with asking Jesus to come into your heart and accepting him as your savior but is just a ritual that we must go through to enable us to enter Heaven